what a fucking hypocrite!!!!
he says i need to get in shape, that he's worried about my health cuz "all you do is sit around all day! you're 19! you should be more energetic!!"
what the fuck!!??
19 year olds are NOT energetic, unless u are a cheerleader
but even then

how is that energetic??

yea fucking right!

there

but what i did isn't good enough for him!

yes

bastard!

shit i'm going to miss him
more then anything
he's my life

i'm working on a sculpture project
only not really
it's a bunch of ready mades that i have to paint
i really don't consider ready mades sculptures
for all u non art people a ready made is an object that you don't create...u go out and buy/find it
for example
my project consists of a crushed coke can, a right high-heal shoe, a bottle, and a strainer...there will soon be cooked pasta in it as well
then i have to find a painting that i like and paint it on the objects
fun stuff
all due thursday
i'll have it done
i have a few hours tomorrow, and all day wednesday to finish it
lotz 'o time :)

ok i'm off to finish working for tonight...ta!

ok
so
scott goes to D&D
and i tell him that when i get bored i'll call him to tell him i'm coming over to hang out with him and his friends
which i do
so i go over
and after about 2 hours of just sitting there i get hungry
i tell scott
it's 12 something am
the guy who is running the game says that he will call a break in the next 30 min
ok
fine
break doesn't happen
12:30
i'm really hungry
"don't worry, we're gonna end early tonight" says the DM
fine
1am
i'm really really hungry and have had enough
i leave
i take scott's keys and am now in his room
they will prabably end in 30 min, go to konover and get food
do u think scott will get me anything??
no
doesn't matter that he knows i'm hungry as all hell
no
he wont
cuz he doesn't think of anybody but himself
he tells me i'm too selfless, that i put people before myself too much
well HE doesn't do it at all
it's all about him in his mind and he thinks of no one but himself
if i was in his shoes, and he left a game i was playing because he was hungry and tired and I KNEW IT, i would go to konover to get food for myself AND for him
why?
because i love him and i knew he was hungry
but would he do that for me
no
no, he will walk in here around 2, happy as a pig in shit cuz he's eaten
and where will i be? waiting here, in his bed
hungry
pissed
tired
and yet goddess i still love him more then anything
i hope he proves me wrong
